data.description: Live in one and rent the other~ which would you choose? Well kept FULL DUPLEX with GREAT VIEWS of Green Park and Pond! Each side has 2 beds/2 baths, SCREENED PORCH, 1 car garage and  New 2022 roof. Right side comes FULLY FURNISHED (EVERYTHING) just bring your toothbrush.  Nothing needed to start earning income! Close to Downtown, Capt. Hirams, the River and warm local Beaches! (All room sizes approx. and to be verified by buyer)
